Actions.Text: AMEND AND RECOMMIT TO HIGHER EDUCATION
COMMITTEE DISCHARGED AND COMMITTED TO RULES

Title: Authorizes an increase in the tuition of out-of-state residents for SUNY environmental science and forestry
Summary: Authorizes an increase in the tuition of out-of-state residents for SUNY environmental science and forestry.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to certain increases in non-resident undergraduate rates of tuition for the state university of New York college of environmental science and forestry
